CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1969 reads: " Exotic Kathy Campbell, a particular favorite of the annual Society's Gala, was in fifth fund-raising show at Carnegie Music Hall. Here she wears a Donald Brooks glittering evening gown, heavily beaded in black with cap to match. "--Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Cathy Campbell modeling full length sleeveless sequined dress with circle pattern and matching turban, posed on stage with metallic surface for Symphony Society Gala
